Republican and Democratic lawmakers pressed US President Donald Trump on Thursday to impose sanctions on Turkey over its purchase of a Russian missile defense system, saying he should follow a law mandating penalties for doing business with Russia's military.White House previously announced removing Turkey from the F-35 fighter jet program. 
